{
  "stem": "17626.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At that-- in-- in Archangel, I do not remember having friends or-- and I don't even know if there were other people with children.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Life was very segregated.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You had your little house, which consisted of a room-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] --your-- your immediate family.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Things were fairly secretive.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I do not recall having a social life, not just for myself but for my parents as well.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "None at all.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "None at all.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nothing at all.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was not-- this was not a place where people lived a normal life.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know what went on, like in the prison where the-- the Russian prisoners were.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But on that [INAUDIBLE] itself, I don't recall ever having books or radio, newspapers, some sort of communication even with other people.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't recall.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I do recall that-- just that hospital and where it stood.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's-- it's a vision that stands in front of my eyes, the forest where it was in proportion to our house.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the life that went on there, food.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A lot of mushrooms.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHING] About A lot of mushrooms.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Mother learned how to-- how to pick the mushrooms because there were many incidences of poison mushrooms and fruits.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Berries, there were a lot of berries.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And during the winter months, it was lean pickings.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In those days, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After that, I-- I-- don't remember hunger to the point of [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] suffering, prolonged suffering.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I do know that my father when we first landed in the [INAUDIBLE], in that area, being not citizens of that area or just being guests of cousins and when we were taken away, we had nothing to take with us.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But the people who lived there, they took whatever products they had to take with them.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
